import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    plt.scatter(data['X'], data['Y'])
    plt.xlabel('X')
    plt.ylabel('Y')
    
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    
    plt.title("What is the relationship between X and Y?", wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()

import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    box_plot = data.boxplot(column='X', by='Series')
    plt.title("What is the relationship between Series and X?")
    plt.suptitle("")
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        box_plot.xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()
